==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Amber
<hw>Am"ber</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>p. p. & p. a.</pos>
<conjf>Ambered</conjf> .]</vmorph> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To scent or flavor
with ambergris; <as>as, <ex>ambered</ex> wine</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To preserve in amber; <as>as, an <ex>ambered</ex>
fly</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Amberboa</ent>⟦br⟧
